    "description": "<p>Huakeong Industries was set up as an independent, one-stop hub for construction services. From taking on comprehensive A&amp;A works, conservation and restoration projects, to partnering established businesses in providing complete design and build solutions, the company has the capability with dedicated resources to see every project to fruition.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Partnering with trusted associated partners, we feature a full suite of cranes, concrete pumps, and other construction equipment from our own homegrown construction equipment and transport logistics business. We value-add and provide enhanced services to every construction project we undertake, spanning from infrastructure, plant, industrial facilities under the full Structural, Architectural and M&amp;E scope of services.</p>\n<p>​</p>\n<p>Our other trusted partners also provide:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Established structural steel fabricator and manufacturer of Prefabricated Prefinished Volumetric Construction (PPVC) products &amp; components</li>\n  <li>Process design and construction of water treatment and other process plants</li>\n  <li>Associate construction materials suppliers for all building construction needs</li>\n</ul>",
